    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Manifestations of motion pictures, stored electronically, in any media or digitized format. Use 'videotapes' to refer specifically to electronic audio-visual recordings stored on tape.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
